<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hold-back">hold back</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>阻挡；阻碍：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>No one can hold back the wheel of history. 
谁也无法阻挡历史的车轮。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was held back by his lack of English.
他不懂英语，这阻碍了他的发展。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>抑制 (感情等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>hold back one's anger
压住怒火</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I had to hold back tears as he left.
他离开的时候，我不得不强忍泪水。</p><footer>2010 全国</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>(使) 犹豫：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She held back from telling him what she thought of him.
她想把自己对他的看法告诉他，但又觉得难以启齿。</p></div></div>